{"word":"G4980 - σχολάζω - scholázō - skhol-ad'-zo - Empty","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">σχολάζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>scholázō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>skhol-ad'-zo"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Empty"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - நேரம் செலவு செய்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. to cease from labor; to loiter"},{"paragraph":"2. to be free from labor, to be at leisure, to be idle"},{"paragraph":"3. to be unoccupied, empty"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G4981 - σχολή - scholḗ - skhol-ay'/4981\">G4981</a>; to <i>take a holiday</i>, that is, <i>be at leisure</i> for (by implication <i>devote oneself</i> wholly to); figuratively to <i>be vacant</i> (of a house): - empty, give self."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"}]}